---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for expensy — Money Leak Detector. Learn how we handle your data. We do not collect, store, or share any personal financial information."
  canonical="https://expensy.com/privacy/"
>
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-1.5">
      <span class="font-visueltpro text-xs tracking-wide text-mist-gray">Legal</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-bradford text-4xl font-medium leading-tight tracking-tight text-cloud-whisper sm:text-5xl">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-2 font-visueltpro text-sm text-ash-accent">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <hr class="my-10 border-white/10" />

    <h2 class="font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      Your privacy matters. This Privacy Policy explains how expensy ("we", "our", or "us") handles your information when you use our Money Leak Detector tool at expensy.com.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">No Data Collection</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      We do not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal financial information you enter into our tool. All calculations happen entirely in your browser — your income, expenses, and analysis results never leave your device.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">No Account Required</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      Our Money Leak Detector does not require account creation, email registration, or any form of personal identification. You can use the full tool anonymously.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">No Cookies for Tracking</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      We do not use cookies or any tracking mechanisms to monitor your behavior, serve ads, or build profiles. Technical cookies required for the basic functioning of the website (such as those set by our static hosting provider) may be present but are not used for data collection purposes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      This website is hosted as a static site. Our hosting provider may collect standard server logs (IP address, browser type, page requested) for operational and security purposes. These logs are not used by us for any analytics or tracking.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-cloud-whisper underline underline-offset-2 decoration-white/20 hover:decoration-white/60">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
